asset.hookText: Michael "Moüse" Bastidas is a well respected graffiti artist from Southern California. Moüse has made an impact on the skate community for his custom designed artwork on grip-tape, "Mousegrip," and has worked closely with PROJECT CANVAS on a variety of initiatives bringing social awareness to the art community. His work and dedication to the brand is the reason he is our Featured Artist for September 2013. Each pair is hand-painted by Mouse himself! These are available now in super limited quantities only at Tilly's. Get a pair now and sink your feet into a piece of art history now at Tillys.com!
